+# Privacy Policy for Tirthofy
+
+Effective date: 2026-03-25
+
+Tirthofy ("we", "our", or "us") provides pilgrimage travel, ride booking, temple service, shopping, hotel, and related support features through the Tirthofy mobile application.
+
+This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and the choices available to users of the app.
+
+## Information We Collect
+
+We may collect the following types of information:
+
+### 1. Account Information
+
+When you create an account or sign in, we may collect:
+
+- Name
+- Email address
+- Password
+
+### 2. Profile Information
+
+When you update your profile, we may collect:
+
+- Mobile number
+- Address
+- Profile photo
+
+### 3. Location Information
+
+If you allow location access, the app may collect your device location to:
+
+- Show your current location on maps
+- Help with ride, travel, or place-related features
+- Improve location-based service results
+
+Location access is optional, and some features may have limited functionality if permission is denied.
+
+### 4. Support and Complaint Information
+
+If you contact support or submit a complaint, we may collect:
+
+- Name
+- Email address
+- Mobile number
+- Subject
+- Message details
+
+### 5. Payment Information
+
+The app supports payment-related features through Razorpay and app backend services. We may store or process:
+
+- Payment order details
+- Payment ID
+- Payment status
+- Amount paid
+- Temple name, puja name, ride, or booking-related payment references
+
+We do not state that full card or bank details are stored by us unless that is explicitly handled by your payment provider and backend.
+
+### 6. Device and App Data
+
+We may collect limited technical information required to operate the app, such as:
+
+- Login session token stored on your device
+- Basic app usage and request metadata needed for security and functionality
+- Notification-related data needed to display local notifications
+
+## How We Use Information
+
+We use collected information to:
+
+- Create and manage user accounts
+- Authenticate users and maintain secure sessions
+- Provide rides, map, pilgrimage, shopping, hotel, and related app features
+- Process and record payments
+- Update user profiles
+- Respond to support requests and complaints
+- Display notifications
+- Improve app performance, reliability, and user experience
+- Prevent misuse, fraud, or unauthorized access
+
+## Permissions Used by the App
+
+Depending on the features you use, the app may request these permissions:
+
+- Internet: to connect to app services, maps, payments, and hosted content
+- Camera: to let users capture or select profile or other supported images
+- Notifications: to show local or app-related notifications
+- Location: to show maps, current location, and location-based results
+
+You can manage permissions from your device settings.
+
+## Sharing of Information
+
+We may share information only as needed with service providers that help us operate the app, such as:
+
+- Payment providers, including Razorpay
+- Cloud image hosting providers, such as Cloudinary, for uploaded images
+- Map and place service providers used for map and location features
+- Backend hosting, infrastructure, or support service providers
+
+We may also disclose information:
+
+- To comply with legal obligations
+- To enforce our terms or protect users, the app, or the public
+- In connection with a business transfer, merger, or reorganization, if applicable
+
+We do not sell personal information.
+
+## Data Storage and Retention
+
+We retain information for as long as needed to provide services, maintain records, resolve disputes, comply with legal obligations, and enforce our agreements.
+
+Some information, such as login session data, may also be stored locally on your device until you sign out or clear app data.
+
+## Data Security
+
+We use reasonable administrative, technical, and organizational measures to protect personal information. However, no method of transmission or storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
+
+## Children's Privacy
+
+This app is not intended for children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe a child has provided personal information, contact us so we can review and delete it where appropriate.
+
+## Your Choices
+
+You may:
+
+- Review and update profile information in the app
+- Control device permissions such as location, camera, and notifications
+- Stop using the app at any time
+
+If you want your account or personal data deleted, contact us using the contact information below.
+
+## Third-Party Services
+
+The app may rely on third-party services that have their own privacy practices, including:
+
+- Razorpay
+- Cloudinary
+- Google Maps and related location services
+
+We encourage users to review the privacy policies of those third-party services as well.
+
+## Changes to This Privacy Policy
+
+We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we do, we will post the updated version with a revised effective date.
+
+## Contact Us
+
+If you have questions, requests, or concerns about this Privacy Policy or your data, contact:
+
+- Company/App name: Tirthofy
+- Email: [replace-with-your-support-email]
+- Address: [replace-with-your-business-address]
+
+## Before Publishing
+
+Replace the placeholder contact email and address before uploading this policy to Google Play Console or publishing it on a public website.
